data.description: ***Priced To Sell*** Brand new carpet installed 11/18/23! ***Seller Offering $5,000 Towards Buyer’s Closing Cost*** Buyers can take over seller’s current rate at 4.25% OR One of our preferred lenders has a loan product that this home qualifies for - 100% financing and no mortgage insurance OR 6.375% with a LENDER PAID 1 YR Buydown to 5.375 for the first year!!!  This home does not disappoint when it comes to space!  This spacious 2-story home has a formal dining with plenty of space to entertain guest along with a large family room with natural light throughout.  To accommodate your cooking needs, this wide open kitchen has plenty of  countertop space, cabinet space and a large breakfast bar area for in-kitchen serving needs.  In the primary bathroom, enjoy a spacious walk-in shower along with a large primary closet ready for someone with tons of clothes!  Upstairs you find this home not only comes with a spacious gameroom, but it even has a media room wired for surround!  The space doesn't stop there, it even has large secondary bedrooms with great closet space!  Efficiency?? This home has you covered with a tankless water heater and a whole house water softener!  This home is located in one of Manor's most prestigious neighborhoods with a golf course, multiple pools, hike & bike trails, convenient access to Highway 290 and downtown Austin!
